R scripts for making components of Figure 3 of Dreos et al. (PLoS Comput Biol. 2021)

Input files:

Position probability matrices

   cons_hg19_K6_s1_1.mat
   cons_hg19_K6_s1_2.mat
   cons_hg19_K6_s1_3.mat
   cons_hg19_K6_s1_4.mat
   cons_hg19_K6_s1_5.mat
   cons_hg19_K6_s1_6.mat

Scripts: 

Unmodified scripts from seqLogo R package downloaded from
http://bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc/src/contrib/seqLogo_1.54.3.tar.gz

   pwm.R
   seqLogo.R

Modified seqLogo2 function for Figure 3

   seqLogo2_fig3.R

Script to generate the sequence logos for Figure 3 in PDF fromat 

   fig3.R (Usage Rscript --vanilla fig3.R)

Output files:

Sequence logos

   fig3_hg19_class1_logo.pdf
   fig3_hg19_class2_logo.pdf
   fig3_hg19_class3_logo.pdf
   fig3_hg19_class4_logo.pdf
   fig3_hg19_class5_logo.pdf
   fig3_hg19_class6_logo.pdf
